name: Crate Cushion
description:
The Crate Cushion fits nicely on top of a milk crate, for a quick easy seating option.  

For storage they fit neatly inside the crate and can be stacked one on top of the other. 

They have a supper padded seat, waterproof finish underneath (perfect for watching sports, picnics, or the back yard).

2 Fabric choices available:  Hessian and Denim.

Available and sold as a single cushion or in a family pack of 4 (4 fit nicely into a crate).  All you need to do is BYO milk crate or any other hard surface for that matter!

The price of this item is for 1 cushion. 

Please ask for pricing on the Family pack by email to funkedupfurniture@gmail.com
